import * as React from 'react' import './App.css'; import GrabStatBlock from "./components/player_statblock" function App() { let statblock = GrabStatBlock.call("statblock") return (
Strength: {statblock.get("str")}
Dexterity: {statblock.get("dex")}
Constitution: {statblock.get("con")}
Intelligence: {statblock.get("int")}
Wisdom: {statblock.get("wis")}
Charisma: {statblock.get("cha")}
); } export default App;
